href=\"https://github.com/JuliaGeometry/Meshes.jl/blob/master/src/vectors.jl\">https://github.com/JuliaGeometry/Meshes.jl/blob/master/src/vectors.jl</a></p>\n<p>Do we need to add a method for <code>StaticArrays.construct_type</code>?</p>\n<p>Appreciate any help.</p>",
